No problem, I think I learned this from the Nerdy Nights sound tutorial.<br />Also if you don't use the length counter but want to unmute Triangle again, you just write any non-zero value to the Counter Reload Value while keeping the Length Counter Halt Flag set:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">  lda #%10000001<br />  sta $4008              ;unmute Triangle<br /></div><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=6013">Pokun</a> — Tue Aug 29, 2017 4:36 am</p><hr />
